{"tid":929233,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"博彩公司開盤賭盧卡古點出醜","createTime":"2018-12-05T12:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T18:21:59.000Z","uid":209679,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4b97e4d3b85330d3ab8eed85d5f2606370fd8477","tid":929233,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Cc1VpAkXQIKsjud0kf1cPQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f3469ea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯中鋒盧卡古今季表現不濟，連外國博彩公司也看不過眼，開出千奇百趣的盤口取笑他。<br />\n<br />\n周三英超曼聯主場迎戰阿仙奴，外國博彩公司Betfair特別為盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）開出多個有趣的盤口，且看最終有多少人夠膽落注。<br />\n<br />\n這些有趣的盤口包括：盧卡古「踩波車」為3.5倍，這個機會不小，而烏龍助攻予阿仙奴球員入波則為34倍。除此之外，這位比利時國腳扭波出界有3倍，而射門撻Q變成界外球，就有8倍。如果這位25歲紅魔中鋒擺烏龍，更有高達51倍，分頭甚佳，似乎他於今場的表現，已被外界睇死。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，盧卡古在上周六英超對修咸頓時建功，打破了長達981分鐘的入球荒，信心可望回升。盧卡古，爭口氣！給大家看看你不是四肢發達，頭腦簡單！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盧9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kWsLmrO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkWsLmrO.png&h=1a4855d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73c17a9bd34e2842b6bc2d4f1e4d52e1a8289e44","tid":929233,"uid":16777,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"射門撻Q變成界外球 呢樣買得過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6cf6d698b1057addb09d7e8651a3766b90dafa","tid":929233,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e3069ab7b416f194e35fe4636c8d3a7df2285","tid":929233,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T12:17:12.000Z"